\par
\b\fs28 10. Conclusion\b0\fs22\par
The FoodHub project successfully merges modern UI design with robust RESTful backend architecture. It satisfies the academic constraints while pushing far beyond by implementing production-adjacent features (like modular architectures, Role-Based Access Control, and relational data integrity). It represents a comprehensive understanding of the Python web development ecosystem.\par
